BEGIN SET NOCOUNT ON;
MERGE INTO [dbo].[Match] AS target USING ( SELECT @MatchId AS MatchId, @MatchDate AS MatchDate, @SecondRound as SecondRound, @CourseId AS CourseId, @TournamentId AS TournamentId ) AS S ON (target.MatchId = S.MatchId) WHEN MATCHED THEN UPDATE SET MatchDate = S.MatchDate, CourseId = S.CourseId, TournamentId = S.TournamentId, SecondRound = S.SecondRound WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN INSERT (MatchDate, CourseId, TournamentId, SecondRound) VALUES (S.MatchDate, S.CourseId, S.TournamentId, S.SecondRound); END
